{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:28:34.341769+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here's the full breakdown of the subcommands registered in this fork's `gita/cmds.json`:\n\n## Subcommands and their underlying `git` commands\n\n| Subcommand | `git` command run | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| **`br`** | `git branch -vv` | — |\n| **`clean`** | `git clean -dfx` | — |\n| **`diff`** | `git diff` | — |\n| **`difftool`** | `git difftool` | ⚠️ **`disable_async`** |\n| **`fetch`** | `git fetch` | ⚠️ **`allow_all`** |\n| **`last`** | `git log -1 HEAD` | — |\n| **`lo`** | `git log --oneline -7` | ⚠️ **`allow_all`** |\n| **`log`** | `git log` | ⚠️ **`disable_async`** |\n| **`merge`** | `git merge @{u}` | — |\n| **`mergetool`** | `git mergetool` | ⚠️ **`disable_async`** |\n| **`patch`** | `git format-patch HEAD~` | — |\n| **`pull`** | `git pull` | ⚠️ **`allow_all`** |\n| **`push`** | `git push` | ⚠️ **`allow_all`** |\n| **`rebase`** | `git rebase` | — |\n| **`reflog`** | `git reflog` | — |\n| **`remote`** | `git remote -v` | — |\n| **`reset`** | `git reset` | — |\n| **`show`** | `git show` | ⚠️ **`disable_async`** |\n| **`stash`** | `git stash` | — |\n| **`stat`** | `git diff --stat` | ⚠️ **`allow_all`** |\n| **`st`** | `git status` | ⚠️ **`allow_all`** |\n| **`tag`** | `git tag -n` | — |\n\n**22 subcommands** total.\n\n### Entries with `allow_all` (6 subcommands)\n\nThese run across *all* registered repositories when invoked without specifying a repo (i.e., they bypass per-repo filtering):\n\n1. **`fetch`** → `git fetch`\n2. **`lo`** → `git log --oneline -7`\n3. **`pull`** → `git pull`\n4. **`push`** → `git push`\n5. **`stat`** → `git diff --stat`\n6. **`st`** → `git status`\n\n### Entries with `disable_async` (4 subcommands)\n\nThese run *synchronously* (one repo at a time, sequentially) instead of in parallel — typically because they require interactive input or a TTY:\n\n1. **`difftool`** → `git difftool`\n2. **`log`** → `git log`\n3. **`mergetool`** → `git mergetool`\n4. **`show`** → `git show`\n\nNo subcommand sets *both* `allow_all` and `disable_async` simultaneously; the two flags appear on disjoint sets of entries.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 766, "prompt_tokens": 6799, "total_tokens": 7565, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 25, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 6016, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0010286826, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0003622626, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00066642}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780864102-WgyRMUQ9bBfnXfscCjWp", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3c5-ae0d-7540-83fd-399726bdee97-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 6799, "output_tokens": 766, "total_tokens": 7565, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 6016}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 25}}}}]}}}
